<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <%- include('../layouts/app/head') %>
    <title>AI Coach | Momentum Fit</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="dashboard-wrapper">
        <%- include('../partials/sidebar') %>
        <div class="main-content" style="height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
            <%- include('../partials/app-header', { title: 'Momentum Intelligence' }) %>

            <div class="content-pad" style="flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; padding-bottom: 20px;">
                
                <div class="card" style="flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding: 0; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 0;">
                    
                    <div style="flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; padding: 20px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px;">
                        
                        <div style="align-self: flex-start; max-width: 80%;">
                            <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: 0 12px 12px 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
                                <p style="color: var(--text-white); margin: 0;">Olá, Caleb! Analisei seu último treino de pernas. Seu volume está 15% acima da semana passada. Como você está se sentindo hoje?</p>
                            </div>
                            <span style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: #666; margin-top: 5px; display: block;">AI Coach • 08:00</span>
                        </div>

                        <div style="align-self: flex-end; max-width: 80%;">
                            <div style="background: var(--neon-primary); color: black; padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: 12px 0 12px 12px;">
                                <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: 500;">Estou um pouco cansado, mas quero treinar. O que sugere?</p>
                            </div>
                            <span style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: #666; margin-top: 5px; display: block; text-align: right;">Você • 08:05</span>
                        </div>

                        <div style="align-self: flex-start; max-width: 80%;">
                            <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); padding: 15px 20px; border-radius: 0 12px 12px 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
                                <p style="color: var(--text-white); margin-bottom: 10px;">Entendido. Vamos ajustar para um treino de **Recuperação Ativa**.</p>
                                <ul style="padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #ccc;">
                                    <li>Redução de carga em 20%</li>
                                    <li>Foco em mobilidade</li>
                                    <li>Cárdio leve (Zona 2)</li>
                                </ul>
                                <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm" style="margin-top: 5px;">Aplicar este ajuste</button>
                            </div>
                            <span style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: #666; margin-top: 5px; display: block;">AI Coach • 08:06</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div style="padding: 20px; background: var(--bg-panel); border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
                        <form style="display: flex; gap: 10px;">
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Digite sua mensagem para a IA..." style="background: var(--bg-input); border: 1px solid #333;">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 50px; padding: 0;"><i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i></button>
                        </form>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
